Package: rifftron
Title: Easily test your graphics with difftron.
Description: rifftron provides tools to make it easy to test graphics,
    using https://difftron.com/ to provide nice visual diffs over time.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 'Hadley Wickham <h.wickham@gmail.com> [aut,cre]'
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
License: GPL-3
Imports:
    httr (>= 0.3),
    RCurl
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
